descriptionHtml:
Allows you to place named chests, like Chest of Armors etc.
This mod is half baked. Any help would be much appreciated.
Its also sort of inconvenient.
How to use :
Once the mod is installed, start the game, open the console and type :
help \"chest\"
You\'ll see a list of new chests. 
Move to the place where you want to put your new chest.
Stand in the spot and type :
player.placeatme (x) 
x is the item code of the chest you want. Dont use brackets.
The chest will spawn at your feet.
To delete a chest, select it in the console and type markfordelete. 
Thats it.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Known bugs (I need help, new modder)
Chests spawn slanted.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Issues
Not at all convenient. (Please help me with this too)
